            <li><strong>RAM:</strong> 1GB</li>
            <li><strong>Storage:</strong> 20GB SSD</li>
            <li><strong>Network:</strong> 100Mbps Bandwidth</li>
            <li><strong>IPv4:</strong> 1</li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> Germany | Poland | France</li>
